{"tid":2411632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英 國 擬 7 月 全 面 重 啟 經 濟 活 動","createTime":"2021-02-17T12:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T14:55:02.000Z","uid":227801,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9f0915a00f3c9903e6a030ab8d7d1ad05f1780","tid":2411632,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2379378/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC7%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2379378%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC7%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2595%259F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN26d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=db3ec4e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2379378/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC7%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95</a><br />\n最後更新時間 17.02.2021 16:01 <br />\n英國《每日郵報》報道，首相約翰遜正考慮逐步撤銷防疫封鎖措施，到7月全面重啟經濟活動。約翰遜將於本月22日公布放寬時間表，報道指4月會先讓較大型的酒店重開，但餐廳及酒吧最快要到5月才可重開，其中酒吧到6月初才可全面重開；部份體育運動，包括高爾夫球及網球活動亦可恢復。至於消閒活動，包括本地旅遊，就要到7月才能全面重開。 報道指，約翰遜屆時亦會宣布，在可見的將來會繼續實行「在家工作」安排，鼓勵僱員可以的話，都盡量留家工作。"},{"pid":"9123175d0a0afff319e976f651cb47d42d733eb9","tid":2411632,"uid":2054,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"香港人全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b30d7fd30cd6ca99ed4b3a1e622a66896a97ec","tid":2411632,"uid":119959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"Gogogo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e08d98ebe7e03908b5d7110fb0f4079916b20d7","tid":2411632,"uid":360404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"